cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM 

This paper deals with computer vision problems such as image matching and stereo vision, which are typically categorized under cs.CV. The paper also discusses the use of detectors and descriptors, which are common in robotics (cs.RO) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of infrared and low contrast images, which are often studied in multimedia (cs.MM).
